Citation.sTitle: Density, Viscosity, and Speed of Sound of Solutions of AOT Reverse Micelles in 2,2,4-Trimethylpentane
Citation.sAbstract: The density, viscosity, and speed of sound for 2,2,4-trimethypentane + sodium bis(2-ethylhexyl) sulfosuccinate (AOT) have been measured. The effect of surfactant concentration upon these physical properties has been analyzed. Different equations employed in the literature have been employed to fit the experimental data.
